{"title":"select randomly one task","markdown":{"headingText":"select randomly one task","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"```{r inclusion of images Reg, echo = FALSE, results = \"hide\", message = FALSE, warning = FALSE}\nlibrary(exams)\ninclude_supplement(\n  c(\n    \"slope-highlighted.svg\",\n    \"residuum-highlighted.svg\",\n    \"intercept-highlighted.svg\",\n    \"x-highlighted.svg\",\n    \"y-highlighted.svg\",\n    \"yhat-highlighted.svg\"\n  ), recursive = TRUE\n)\n\nlist_tasks <-\n  list(\n    list(\n      image = \"slope-highlighted.svg\",\n      answers = c(\n        \"Steigung\",\n        \"b₁\",\n        \"Slope\",\n        \"Anstieg\",\n        \"Gibt an, um wie viel sich y im Durchschnitt unterscheidet, wenn x sich um eine Einheit unterscheidet.\"\n      )\n    ),\n    list(\n      image = \"residuum-highlighted.svg\",\n      answers = c(\n        \"Residuum\",\n        \"ε\",\n        \"Error\",\n        \"Differenz zwischen beobachtetem und vorhergesagtem Wert.\"\n      )\n    ),\n    list(\n      image = \"intercept-highlighted.svg\",\n      answers = c(\n        \"Achsenabschnitt\",\n        \"b₀\",\n        \"Intercept\",\n        \"Wert von ŷ, wenn x gleich 0 ist.\"\n      )\n    ),\n    list(\n      image = \"x-highlighted.svg\",\n      answers = c(\"xᵢ\", \"x-Wert\", \"Ausprägung der unabhängigen Variable\")\n    ),\n    list(\n      image = \"y-highlighted.svg\",\n      answers = c(\"yᵢ\", \"y-Wert\", \"Ausprägung der abhängigen Variable\")\n    ),\n    list(\n      image = \"yhat-highlighted.svg\",\n      answers = c(\n        \"ŷᵢ\",\n        \"Vorhergesagtes yᵢ\",\n        \"Predicted yᵢ\",\n        \"Ausprägung der abhängigen Variable, die durch das Modell für xᵢ vorhergesagt wird.\"\n      )\n    )\n  )\nselected_task <- sample(list_tasks, 1)[[1]]\n\n# cocenate all answers in list_task \nanswerlist <- c(\n  list_tasks[[1]]$answers,\n  list_tasks[[2]]$answers,\n  list_tasks[[3]]$answers,\n  list_tasks[[4]]$answers,\n  list_tasks[[5]]$answers,\n  list_tasks[[6]]$answers\n)\n\n# create logical vector indication true answers by asking if answers in answerlist are in selected_task$answers\nsolution <- answerlist %in% selected_task$answers\n```\n\n\nQuestion\n========\n### Übung {{< iconify fa7-solid:person-digging >}} {.unnumbered .h3short}\nWelche der Begriffe passen zum [grün]{style='color:#267326; font-weight: bold;'} hervorgehobenen Teil der folgenden Abbildung?\n\n![](`r selected_task$image`){width=\"300px\"}\n\n\n```{r questionlist regelements, echo = FALSE, results='asis'}\nanswerlist(\n  answerlist,\n  markup = \"markdown\"\n)\n```\n\n\n\nMeta-information\n================\nexname: Grundbegriffe Regression erkennen\nextype: mchoice\nexsolution: `r exams::mchoice2string(solution)`\nexshuffle: 5","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"live-html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"live-html","base-format":"html","extension-name":"live"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":"auto","echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"knitr"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":fal